闻名。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="雪之协会|官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pDak4qLyF4Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>据<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/netflix-new-film-society-of-the-snow-bayona-b2472560.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《独立报》报道</em></a>，巴约纳在拍摄前参观了坠机现场，并确保幸存者家属批准改编。</p><p>巴约纳评价他的演员们：“演员们很勇敢，全心全意地表演，经历了幸存者可能会忍受的寒冷和饥饿。”</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/rings-of-power-lord-of-the-rings-galadriel-boat-scene-ja-bayona-3557298">巴亚纳分享了一些有关<em>《指环王：权力指环》</em>中场景的有趣信息</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/this-spanish-language-survival-thriller-is-top-of-netflix-globally-3568624">这部西班牙语生存惊悚片在 Netflix 全球排名第一的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
